Chacha Bhatija is an awesome movie. The title means Uncle and Nephew (Dharmendra and Randhir Kapoor respectively). The both did not know that they were related and the Nephew though his father was dead. It is comedy,  suspense, and action, musical thriller. One of the best ever Indian movies.  Especially for kids.
